casebody.data:
JPRC, INC. t/a Liquid Assets, Petitioner-Petitioner,
v.
NEW JERSEY DEPARTMENT OF LABOR AND WORKFORCE DEVELOPMENT, Respondent-Respondent. C-434 September Term 2017
079984 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 13, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001736-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
